member.name: T:DataJBC.CTemperature
member.summary: This class represents a temperature value. It stores the temperature in UTI units that can easily be converted into CELSIUS and FAHRENHEIT degrees using the ToCelsius() and ToFahrenheit() methods. The temperature value can also be set in CELSIUS or FAHRENHEIT by using the InCelsius() or InFahrenheit() methods.
